p: \rWe have you now, Riolu!\nThere's nowhere to run!
\rWhat do you think you're doing?\nCan't you see you're scaring it?
\rWill the two of you deal with them, please?\nDo it quickly, we have a Riolu to catch!
\bThe Abyssal Cult will crush you here!
\rHmph! How on earth could you lose?\nYou two have the best Pokemon the Abyssal Cult have to offer!
\rWhy do I always need to clean up after your mistakes?\nI'll deal with the children in a second.\nFor now...
\rAww, how sweet.\nThe mother came to protect her little child.

Now quick, grunts!
You've heard the rumors about this Lucario!
You know why we're here!
We need to catch it quickly, before it-
\rGrunts! Run, now!\nWe can't handle Lucario in this form!
\rI only came here because I heard about this ruin and I thought it would be interesting to explore...
\rI'm glad I came in time.\nThose people were from the Abyssal Cult.
\rI know they worship Kyogre, but not much else.
\r...Mega Evolution, huh?\nI've heard of it before.\nI don't fully understand it, but it seems to be a form where Pokemon become even more powerful than before.
\rBut I remember reading that Mega Evolution requires a close bond between Trainer and Pokemon.
\rI wonder how that Lucario was able to do it, then?
\rI need to go research this more.\nI'll see you around, \pn.\nDon't forget, we're still in a race!
\rBwa ha ha ha ha!\nWe have you cornered, Riolu! There's nowhere to run!
\rJust stop running, Riolu! You're ours now!
\rHuh? Who daaaaares stand in the way of the Abyssal Cult?!
\rWill the two of you deal with them, please? We have a Riolu to catch!
\bThe Abyssal Cult will crush you here!
\rHmph! How on earth could you lose?\nYou two have the best Pokemon we have to offer!
\rWhy do I always need to clean up after your mistakes?\nI'll deal with them myself in a second.\nFor now...
\rAww, how sweet... but your mother won't rescue you!

Now quick, grunts!
You've heard the rumors about this Lucario!
You know why we're here!
We need to catch it quickly, before it-
\rHow... that's impossible!\nThat shouldn't be able to happen!
\rQuick, let's get out of here! We can't handle a Mega Lucario!
\rI only came here because I heard about this ruin, and I thought it would be interesting to explore.
\rI'm glad I came in time.\nThose people were from the Abyssal Cult.
\rFrom what I can tell, they're pretty similar to Team Aqua from Hoenn.\nThey're trying to capture the legendary Pokemon, Kyogre.
\r...Mega Evolution, huh?\nI've heard of it before.\nI don't fully understand it, but it seems to be a form where Pokemon become even more powerful than before.
\rBut I remember reading that it requires a close bond between Trainer and Pokemon.
\rI wonder how that Lucario was able to do it, then?
\rI need to go research this more.\nI'll see you around, \pn.\nDon't forget- we're still racing to Suntouched City!
An item appeared from the past!
